{"1172620": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Sea of Thieves: 2025 Edition", "steam_appid": 1172620, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [2838630, 2838640, 3444920, 3444930, 3533300, 3937210], "detailed_description": "<h1>New This Season</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/8e4ce3249526f75101488c2265a5afe3.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Smugglers\u2019 League have crossed the Devil\u2019s Shroud! This mob of miscreants have a keen eye for the finer things in life, and of course the light fingers needed to acquire them from under the original owner\u2019s nose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The exact nature of their business on the Sea of Thieves is a closely guarded secret, but they\u2019ve got some work for pirates who are looking to make a little extra gold while fighting off rival crews along the way. So if you want to get a foot in the door with the Smugglers, start by searching for their Hideouts\u2026 \u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/292d90688f7d7919065c210d5af6dda3.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the Mystery </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smugglers are, unsurprisingly, a tight-lipped bunch, but surely you can unearth some clues regarding their plans somewhere across the seas. Maybe a pirate with a keen eye and inquisitive nature could get to the bottom of their machinations\u2026 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/64870dbd0d621536a4f09b3d601c7a40.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smugglers\u2019 Hideouts </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you\u2019re operating off the books, it wouldn\u2019t do to be seen around the Outposts. Instead, The Smugglers\u2019 League contacts have settled down in hidden Hideouts across the map, protected by concealed traps that you\u2019ll need to avoid (or even use against your rivals) to ensure a safe delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/3ce362fcc1b54deb5c22cfb250a68226.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smuggle Contraband</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the League still getting to grips with life on the Sea of Thieves, they\u2019re in need of a hand to get their cargo where it needs to be. Available in High Seas, Smugglers\u2019 Route Runs can be attempted from your Quest Table and take place along a golden route which will change each Season \u2013 a route that's also marked on other ships\u2019 Map Tables, raising the challenge of reaching your destination with all cargo intact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elsewhere, finding a Smuggler-branded Message in a Bottle also offers the opportunity to take on a Smugglers\u2019 Run. These emergent Voyages can propose a variety of routes with even more exotic cargo, but all focus on sneaking precious, fragile wares from one Smugglers\u2019 Hideout to another. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/3ce45b3dee86b02c109b9f94b0689acf.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clandestine Cargo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rather than standard treasure chests and skulls, The Smugglers\u2019 League seek rarer kinds of loot from Fine Art and high-value rum to extremely potent Black Powder Barrels! Get your hands on these and you\u2019ll need to handle them with care: rum bottles will shatter if damaged, and while Black Powder Barrels can withstand a little punishment, their detonation packs more of a punch than any other explosive on the waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/c255999fa4b0332fe0ae8589e1b66d10.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An Evolving Sandbox</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hideouts aren\u2019t the only mark of the League\u2019s arrival. Smugglers\u2019 Shipwrecks can be found dotting the waves this Season, loaded with rare and desirable cargo that\u2019s well worth a detour to salvage. Roving Skeleton Ships have already been out there claiming some of this cargo, and scattered items can also be found washed up on shorelines, provided another keen-eyed crew doesn\u2019t find them first!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/2c277b85e4d626d2d4f9afa2615ecf82.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Seasonal Rewards</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new Season means a brand new set of rewards, unlocked by climbing through 100 levels of Renown! Earn cosmetics, gold, Doubloons and even Ancient Coins as you rise through the ranks by living the pirate life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/3aad148e2de3c3b5b1b8805224051352.poster.avif?t=1755260861\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/3aad148e2de3c3b5b1b8805224051352.webm?t=1755260861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/3aad148e2de3c3b5b1b8805224051352.mp4?t=1755260861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sea of Thieves offers the essential pirate experience, from sailing and fighting to exploring and looting \u2013 everything you need to live the pirate life and become a legend in your own right. With no set roles, you have complete freedom to approach the world, and other players, however you choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/7284ea4e6ff2ba4782435cab15ea2094.poster.avif?t=1755260861\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/7284ea4e6ff2ba4782435cab15ea2094.webm?t=1755260861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/7284ea4e6ff2ba4782435cab15ea2094.mp4?t=1755260861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you\u2019re voyaging as a group or sailing solo, you\u2019re bound to encounter other crews in this shared world adventure \u2013 but will they be friends or foes, and how will you respond?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/fd70d79590545d2eb1712863d8079dcb.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Vast Open World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast open world filled with unspoiled islands and underwater kingdoms. Take on quests to hunt for lost loot, forge a reputation with the Trading Companies and battle foes from Phantoms and Ocean Crawlers to Megalodons and the mighty Kraken. Try your hand at fishing, make maps to your own buried treasure or choose from hundreds of other optional goals and side-quests!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/12b171e0691f14f3c35ff6bab171b614.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Game That\u2019s Always Growing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each Season bringing in new game features every three months alongside regular in-game Events, Sea of Thieves is a service-based game that\u2019s still growing and evolving. Check back regularly to see what free content has been newly added, and see how far you can climb through each Season\u2019s 100 levels of Renown to earn special rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/890edf9bfcad4ee8fe3ab4b33e4a4ab1.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become Legend</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your journey to become a Pirate Legend you\u2019ll amass loot, build a reputation and define a unique personal style with your hard-earned rewards. Adventurer. Explorer. Conqueror. What will your legend be?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/ddab2ef069bccfa2a2f6984e37a61c27.poster.avif?t=1755260861\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/ddab2ef069bccfa2a2f6984e37a61c27.webm?t=1755260861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/ddab2ef069bccfa2a2f6984e37a61c27.mp4?t=1755260861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/f9c4e37abf4f882e6e8c1f0d868dc748.webp?t=1755260861\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/4d8b89bce7993c33f1140a0765f690f2.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sea of Thieves: Premium Edition</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Premium Edition includes:\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the content in the Base and Deluxe Editions\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dire Dark Warsmith Flag, Hull, Figurehead, Sails, Cannons, Cannon Flare, Capstan, Wheel, Collector\u2019s Figurehead, Collector\u2019s Sails, Ship\u2019s Crest and Costume Set\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1000 Ancient Coins for use in the Pirate Emporium</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/85149fd144660ab13807e6e9189ee872.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sea of Thieves: Deluxe Edition</strong> \u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 2025 Deluxe Edition includes:\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the content in the Base Edition\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parrot Hat, Jacket, Dress, Boots, Belt, Trousers and Gloves, and 10,000 gold to spend at the Outposts\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dire Dark Warsmith Pistol, Blunderbuss, Eye of Reach, Cutlass, Double Barrel Pistol, Throwing Knives, Grapple Gun and Blowpipe\u00a0\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172620/extras/adf5e151368a123dcd4bd49ef5a8ab97.avif?t=1755260861\" width=780 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sea of Thieves</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 2025 Base Edition includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full game\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video c